Package photos.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Album
    Album class contains String Name, ArrayList Photos, int numOfPhotos, SimpleDateFormat oldestDate, SimpleDateFormat newestDate, String coverpath as attributes.
    CustomTags
    CustomTags class is a subclass of Tags class.
    Photo
    toString() method returns a formatted String of tag name, tag type on a single line, in a format that can be printed next to its respective Photo
    Tags
    Tags class represents Tag objects with attributes of Strings for the tag type and tag name, and implements Serializable so that the tags remain associated to their respective photos across sessions.
    User
    User class creates instance of User object with constructor.
    Users
    Users class is comprised of an ArrayList of users that remains static and implements Serializable so that the list of users carries through all sessions.
